---
title: Choriqueso Burgers with Spicy Crema and Kale Caesar
description: Smoky, spicy, cheesy and on the table in just 20 minutes – this Choriqueso Burger is bound to have you looking forward to dinnertime! Simple chorizo patties let this flavourful meat shine, with a blanket of creamy, melty mozzarella on top to bring the burger together. If that isn't enough, we've added a lemony kale Caesar side salad to sweeten the deal. Get cookin'!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/choriqueso-burgers-12e4ea4f.jpg
